'''大衛·馬丁·達爾'''（{{lang-en|David Martin Dahl}}，{{bd|1994年|4月1日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的外野手，目前效力於密爾瓦基釀酒人，先前曾效力於洛磯和遊騎兵兩隊。
==職業生涯==
===科羅拉多洛磯===
[[2012年美國職棒大聯盟選秀|2012年美國職棒大聯盟選秀]]，洛磯隊在第一輪第10順位選進達爾。<ref name=draft>{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20120604&content_id=32757904&vkey=news_mlb&c_id=mlb|title=Rockies snag prep outfielder David Dahl with 10th overall pick in First-Year Player Draft|work=MLB.com|date=June 4, 2012|accessdate=July 25, 2016|archive-date=2012-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120618064706/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20120604&content_id=32757904&vkey=news_mlb&c_id=mlb|dead-url=no}}</ref>達爾選擇放棄就讀奧本大學，而跟洛磯隊簽約。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://highschoolsports.al.com/news/article/7827201519372279376/oak-mountain-star-david-dahl-signs-26m-deal-with-rockies/|title=Oak Mountain star David Dahl signs $2.6M deal with Rockies|work=AL.com|accessdate=July 25, 2016|archive-date=2016-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160809140133/http://highschoolsports.al.com/news/article/7827201519372279376/oak-mountain-star-david-dahl-signs-26m-deal-with-rockies/|dead-url=no}}</ref>他在新人聯盟就繳出3成79打擊率，外帶9轟與57分打點的成績拿下開拓者聯盟的MVP。<ref name=mlb.com>{{cite web|url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/67249274/rockies-outfield-prospect-david-dahl-eager-to-move-forward-after-rough-season/|title=Rockies outfield prospect David Dahl eager to move forward after rough season|work=MLB.com|accessdate=July 25, 2016|archive-date=2016-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161009094216/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/67249274/rockies-outfield-prospect-david-dahl-eager-to-move-forward-after-rough-season/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年，達爾成為洛磯隊的第二名新秀。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.baseballamerica.com/today/prospects/rankings/organization-top-10-prospects/2013/2614567.html|title=BaseballAmerica.com: Prospects: Rankings: Organization Top 10 Prospects: 2013 Colorado Rockies Top 10 Prospects|work=Baseball America|accessdate=July 25, 2016|archive-date=2017-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170504110318/http://www.baseballamerica.com/today/prospects/rankings/organization-top-10-prospects/2013/2614567.html/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2014年7月，他升上高階1A。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.denverpost.com/2014/07/25/rockies-prospect-david-dahl-shows-promise-in-promotion-to-modesto-nuts/|title=Rockies prospect David Dahl shows promise in promotion to Modesto Nuts|work=The Denver Post|date=July 25, 2014|accessdate=July 25, 2016|archive-date=2016-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160817194736/http://www.denverpost.com/2014/07/25/rockies-prospect-david-dahl-shows-promise-in-promotion-to-modesto-nuts/|dead-url=no}}</ref>他在那邊的打擊率為2成99，並敲出14轟與21次盜壘成功。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.idahostatesman.com/sports/mlb/boise-hawks/article40867419.html|title=Rockies’ top prospect will soon join Boise Hawks|work=Idaho Statesman|accessdate=July 25, 2016}}</ref>

2015年3月28日，達爾在一次追球過程中與隊友發生碰撞，造成他脾臟撕裂傷。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/rockies-david-dahl-opts-to-have-spleen-removed-for-quicker-return/|title=Rockies' David Dahl opts to have spleen removed for quicker return|publisher=[[CBS_Sports|CBS Sports]]|accessdate=July 25, 2016|archive-date=2016-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160917215053/http://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/rockies-david-dahl-opts-to-have-spleen-removed-for-quicker-return/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2016年，達爾受邀參加大聯盟春訓。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20160211&content_id=164282372&fext=.jsp&vkey=news_milb|title=Rockies invite Dahl, Hoffman, McMahon: Club's No. 3, 4, 5 prospects headed to Major League Spring Training|first=Tyler|last=Maun|work=MiLB.com|date=February 11, 2016|accessdate=July 27, 2016|archive-date=2016-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160914142053/http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20160211&content_id=164282372&fext=.jsp&vkey=news_milb|dead-url=no}}</ref>這年他在2A的打擊率為2成78，並敲出13轟與45分打點。升上3A後，他頂替受傷的Austin Meadows參加未來之星明星賽。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.al.com/sports/index.ssf/2016/07/oak_mountains_david_dahl_to_pl.html|title=Oak Mountain's David Dahl to play in Sunday's All-Star Futures Game|work=AL.com|accessdate=July 25, 2016|archive-date=2017-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170930131234/http://www.al.com/sports/index.ssf/2016/07/oak_mountains_david_dahl_to_pl.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>7月25日，達爾登上大聯盟，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.denverpost.com/2016/07/24/david-dahl-one-of-rockies-top-prospects-will-get-called-up-monday-to-the-majors/|title=David Dahl, one of Rockies’ top prospects, will get called up to majors Monday|work=The Denver Post|date=July 24, 2016|accessdate=July 25, 2016|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108204900/http://www.denverpost.com/2016/07/24/david-dahl-one-of-rockies-top-prospects-will-get-called-up-monday-to-the-majors/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.denverpost.com/2016/07/25/david-dahl-starts-in-left-bats-6th-in-highly-anticipated-rockies-debut/|title=David Dahl starts in left field, bats sixth in highly anticipated big-league debut with Rockies|first=Patrick|last=Saunders|work=The Denver Post|date=July 25, 2016|accessdate=July 25, 2016|archive-date=2019-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190328192441/https://www.denverpost.com/2016/07/25/david-dahl-starts-in-left-bats-6th-in-highly-anticipated-rockies-debut/|dead-url=no}}</ref>並在初登場面對[[尤凡尼·賈亞爾多|尤凡尼·賈亞爾多]]敲出大聯盟首安。隨後他締造了連續17場比賽敲出安打的紀錄，追平了1941年Chuck Aleno寫下的菜鳥球員初登板最多連續安打場次紀錄。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.al.com/sports/index.ssf/2016/08/oak_mountains_david_dahl_ties.html|title=Oak Mountain's David Dahl ties Major League hitting record|first=Mark|last=Inabinett|work=AL.com|date=August 11, 2016|accessdate=August 11, 2016|archive-date=2018-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181009211526/https://www.al.com/sports/index.ssf/2016/08/oak_mountains_david_dahl_ties.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/195307058/rockies-david-dahls-hit-streak-comes-to-end/|title=Dahl's 17-game streak to start career ends|first=Thomas|last=Harding|work=MLB.com|date=August 13, 2016|accessdate=August 15, 2016|archive-date=2017-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170930084724/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/195307058/rockies-david-dahls-hit-streak-comes-to-end/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2017年春訓，達爾的肋骨出現疲勞性骨折，最後造成他該季報銷。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/rockies/news/rockies-david-dahl-cleared-to-swing-bat/c-264232684|title=Outfielder Dahl (rib/back) cleared to swing bat: 23-year-old outfielder looking to make impact for Rockies in 2018|first=Thomas|last=Harding|work=MLB.com|date=January 4, 2018|accessdate=January 8, 2018|archive-date=2018-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180109064155/https://www.mlb.com/rockies/news/rockies-david-dahl-cleared-to-swing-bat/c-264232684|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年，達爾出賽100場比賽，打擊率為3成02，並敲出15轟與61分打點。他不僅首度入選明星賽，還在明星賽敲出一支安打。<ref>{{citeweb|url=https://www.shelbycountyreporter.com/2019/07/10/former-omhs-star-david-dahl-goes-1-for-1-in-all-star-debut/|title=Former OMHS star David Dahl goes 1-for-1 in All-Star debut|first=Alec|last=Etheredge|publisher=Shelby County Reporter|date=July 10, 2019|accessdate=May 28, 2020|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128221055/https://www.shelbycountyreporter.com/2019/07/10/former-omhs-star-david-dahl-goes-1-for-1-in-all-star-debut/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2019年，達爾出賽100場比賽，打擊率3成02，並敲出15轟與61分打點。這年他還首度入選明星賽。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.shelbycountyreporter.com/2019/07/10/former-omhs-star-david-dahl-goes-1-for-1-in-all-star-debut/|title=Former OMHS star David Dahl goes 1-for-1 in All-Star debut|first=Alec|last=Etheredge|publisher=Shelby County Reporter|date=July 10, 2019|accessdate=May 28, 2020|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128221055/https://www.shelbycountyreporter.com/2019/07/10/former-omhs-star-david-dahl-goes-1-for-1-in-all-star-debut/|dead-url=no}}</ref>不過隔年他的打擊率僅1成83，並打回8分打點。球季結束後他未獲得球隊續約，成為自由球員。
===德州遊騎兵===
2020年12月，達爾與遊騎兵簽下1年270萬美元的合約。<ref>https://www.washingtonpost.com/sports/mlb/rangers-sign-of-david-dahl-to-27-million-1-year-contract/2020/12/15/d008e29a-3f1e-11eb-b58b-1623f6267960_story.html</ref>2021年，他的打擊率僅有2成10，並敲出4轟與18分打點，因此球隊在8月2日將他指定讓渡。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2021/08/rangers-dfa-david-dahl.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-08-03 |archive-date=2021-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210808013303/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2021/08/rangers-dfa-david-dahl.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
===密爾瓦基釀酒人===
2021年8月17日，達爾和釀酒人簽下小聯盟合約。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2021/08/brewers-sign-david-dahl-release-kevin-kramer.html|title=Brewers Sign David Dahl to Minor League Deal|access-date=2021-12-05|archive-date=2021-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211205081347/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2021/08/brewers-sign-david-dahl-release-kevin-kramer.html}}</ref>
